Techspardha is the Techno-managerial festival of nit Kurukshetra which started in 1995 as "Technospect" (later changed to Literati). It has a variety of events (60+) ranging from Technical Paper Presentations, Robotics, Software Development, Aero-modelling, quizzes to managerial events like Debates, Advertising etc. The year 2013 marked the golden jubilee of nit Kurukshetra and thus the mega techno-managerial festival was re-christened "Techspardha". TS'16 attracted participation from over 350 colleges across the country. This year, we aim to take this festival to even bigger heights with extensive focus on india's contribution to technology.

Theme

The word space has a certain ring to it. It is perhaps the most arcane realm ever encountered by mankind. Audacious efforts are being made as we speak to explore this realm and lucidly understand it. Being inspired by the concept of space this Techspardha is based on space and the infinite possibilities, it offers. It is time to showcase our nerve and commandeer through the milky way named Techspardha.
